trans-unit.source: Exposes the items in the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items" /> collection of a <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector" /> to UI Automation.
trans-unit.target: <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector" />의 <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items" /> 컬렉션에 있는 항목을 UI 자동화에 노출합니다.

trans-unit.source: The item object that is associated with this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.SelectorItemAutomationPeer" />.

The <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.SelectorAutomationPeer" /> that is associated with the <see cref="T:System.Windows.Controls.Primitives.Selector" /> that holds the <see cref="P:System.Windows.Controls.ItemsControl.Items" /> collection.
Provides initialization for base class values when they are called by the constructor of a derived class.
trans-unit.target: 파생 클래스의 생성자에서 호출될 때 기본 클래스 값의 초기화를 제공합니다.

trans-unit.source: Gets the control pattern that is associated with the specified <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface" />.

If <paramref name="patternInterface" /> is <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Selection" />, this method returns the current instance of this <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.SelectorItemAutomationPeer" />.
trans-unit.target: <paramref name="patternInterface" />가 <see cref="F:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.PatternInterface.Selection" />이면 이 메서드는 이 <see cref="T:System.Windows.Automation.Peers.SelectorItemAutomationPeer" />의 현재 인스턴스를 반환합니다.
